            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1887-03-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1887-03-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="614" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d614">
                <head>No. 614.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Curry</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1887-03-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">March</hi> 11,
                            1887</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Bayard informs Mr. Curry that the Government of the United States accepts
                        the extension proposed by the Government of Spain of the duration of the
                        agreement of October 27 until June 30.</p>
            </div>
